<inglise> Whereas it is appropriate to amend the Financial Regulation of 21 December 1977 applicable to the general budget of the European Communities (5), hereinafter referred to as the 'Financial Regulation', in order to take account of the start of the third phase of economic and monetary union; </inglise>
